Framed Prints

Bring a touch of historical grandeur to your home with the Media Storehouse Framed Print of the Wedding of Crown Prince Frederick William of Prussia and Princess Louise of Mecklenburg-Strelitz. This stunning, color lithograph by the German School, depicts the opulent wedding ceremony held in the Royal Palace of Berlin on December 24, 1793. Witness the elegance and majesty of the occasion as the future King of Prussia and his bride exchange vows in this beautifully detailed and authentic reproduction. Add this striking piece to your collection and relive the rich history of the past.
